title: Skateboarding with Kelly Hart
itunes:title: Skateboarding with Kelly Hart
description:
In this episode, the team discusses skateboarding with professional skateboarder and co-host of the podcast "The Nine Club", Kelly Hart.

Follow Kelly on Instagram @KellyHart .

Make sure to check. out his podcast "The Nine Club" on Youtube and wherever you listen to podcasts.

Our merch store is now live! Go to idontknowaboutthat.com for shirts, hoodies, mugs, and more!

Subscribe to our Patreon at patreon.com/IDKAT for ad free episodes, bonus episodes, and more exclusive perks! Tiers start at just $2!
